<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="253" type="observations">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="253">Observations.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="253">
The ICZN stablishes that a 
<normalizedToken originalValue="species’">species'</normalizedToken>
epithet should agree with the gender of the genus. Since 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Lopes &amp; Carpenter &amp; Noll" authorityYear="2021" class="Insecta" family="Eumenidae" genus="Ischnocoelia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Ischnocoelia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="253" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="253">Ischnocoelia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is female and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Lopes &amp; Carpenter &amp; Noll" authorityYear="2021" baseAuthorityName="Fabricius" baseAuthorityYear="1804" class="Insecta" family="Eumenidae" genus="Zethus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zethus" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="253" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="253">Zethus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, male, there is a mandatory spelling change (Art. 34.2, ICNZ) for names that are female. While most of the specific epithets could simply be converted into masculine form due to the new combination under 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Lopes &amp; Carpenter &amp; Noll" authorityYear="2021" baseAuthorityName="Fabricius" baseAuthorityYear="1804" class="Insecta" family="Eumenidae" genus="Zethus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zethus" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="253" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="253">Zethus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and kept similar to the current valid one, a new name had to be given to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Lopes &amp; Carpenter &amp; Noll" authorityYear="2021" class="Insecta" family="Eumenidae" genus="Ischnocoelia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Ischnocoelia ferruginea" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="253" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ferruginea">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="253">Ischnocoelia ferruginea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
due to homonomy. The new combinations of other species are given in the Suppl. material 3.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
